reviewText: I bought it for my grandson because he loves watching the Pup and Scooby as they grown up on TV.

if yu love Scooby and the gang, then you will also love Scooby and the gang when thy are little kids.  so far ive purchased series 1, 2,3, 4, 5,6 ,and 7. my grand daughter is ecstatic, when she comes to visit shesays,  pappy, put little Scooby in.  you have kids, get these,  they are great.  terry chubb

I remember watching this show all the time when I was younger.  Then, when the cartoon was removed from TV, I had no way of finding it and watching it again. Thanks to this DVD, I can let my collection of this show grow.

Can't imagine giving Scooby-Doo anything but 5 stars.  My 4-year-old son, as well as my husband and myself, LOVE Scooby-Doo.  It is something that adults can still enjoy.  This DVD has 5 episodes.  I like the Pup versions because I never saw them as a kid, so they are new to me, and are no less quality than the original Scooby-Doos.  The picture quality was never enhanced from the original versions, so it isn't that great.  But, if you like Scooby-Doo, it is no big deal.

My son loves Scooby-Doo, but would scard when he watched the cartoons.  I recalled the Pup name Scooby-Doo from when I was kid and purchased this DVD for him.  He loves it and doesn't have me check under the bed for monsters anymore.

My youngest has been a Scooby Doo Fan for most of her young life. Bringing out the Pup named Scooby series has made her one happy little girl. She has all the Scooby videos. Now she can start collecting the Pup movies. This one is her favorite.
Great series. My kid loves them all. Nice for Scooby Doo fans
I received it earlier than I thought awesome great and fast delivery
It's Scooby Doo! What else is there to say? It's awesome!
This is the only place that I have found the "Pup".  Grandson just loves it! They aren't showing these any more on tv.
